Sentencas: Electrical performance of a 3D planar solid oxide fuel cell, with ammonia internal decomposition as fuel and yttrium-stabled zirconia as electrolyte, has been simulated numerically, incorporated with the software Comsol Multiphysics.
Titulo: Numerical Simulation on the Performance of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with Direct Ammonia Internal Decomposition

Sentencas: With the help of the software, gas concentration distribution in an anode/cathode channel as well as current density distribution was demonstrated.
Titulo: Numerical Simulation on the Performance of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with Direct Ammonia Internal Decomposition

Sentencas: The poor gas concentration distribution in the cathode channel is mainly responsible for the poor current density distribution.
Titulo: Numerical Simulation on the Performance of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with Direct Ammonia Internal Decomposition

Sentencas: Furthermore, the effect of current density on the solid oxide fuel cell ohmic and activation overpotential was analyzed.
Titulo: Numerical Simulation on the Performance of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with Direct Ammonia Internal Decomposition

Sentencas: The simulation results conform to the data in the experimental literature well.
Titulo: Numerical Simulation on the Performance of a Solid Oxide Fuel Cell with Direct Ammonia Internal Decomposition
